### 1) 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "tran01", "password": "test1234", "name": "Tran", "email": "tran@knu.ac.kr", "affiliation": "컴퓨터학부" }

### 2) 로그인 (accessToken 복사)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "tran01", "password": "test1234" }

### 3) 공간 목록 (공개)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rooms

### 4) 공간 현황 (시설 + 점유 시간대)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/1/availability

### 5) 예약 (로그인 토큰 필요)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{ "roomId": 1, "startTime": "2026-06-10T10:00:00", "endTime": "2026-06-10T12:00:00" }

### 6) 내 예약
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/me
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 7) 관리자 로그인 (admin / admin1234)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "admin", "password": "admin1234" }

### 8) 관리자: 공간 생성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/rooms
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>

{ "name": "기숙사 독서실", "location": "기숙사 B동", "capacity": 1, "active": true, "facilityIds": [1] }

### 9) 관리자: Google Drive 백업
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/backup
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>
